        Changes
        =======
        
        0.4 (2015-05-24)
        ----------------
        
        - Simplified creation of local components
        
        - Added setting option `components_path`
        
        - Changed to PEP 420 namespace package
        
        
        0.3 (2015-01-10)
        ----------------
        
        - Support multiple `bower_components` directories
        
        
        0.2 (2015-01-09)
        ----------------
        
        - Added documentation
        
        - Added setting options via ini file
        
        
        0.1 (2015-01-06)
        ----------------
        
        - Initial release
        
